Create a program Simple Student Tracker (Functions Version)

Data Types:
name (string), scores (list), is_active (boolean)

Functions:
add_score(scores, score) → add score to list and print updated list
average_score(scores) → return average score
get_status(scores) → return "Passed" if average ≥ 70 else "Failed"
activate(is_active) → set to True
deactivate(is_active) → set to False
get_info(name, scores, is_active) → return student info
